Context: The George Brown College offers fully online programs in the academic areas of Business, Computer Technology, and Media & Performing Arts. Potential students can join live, synchronous classes led by experienced faculty. For more information on specific programs available online, visit the Online Programs webpage. Contact information: 416-415-2000 (local), 1-800-265-2002 (toll-free in Canada and USA), ask.george@georgebrown.ca (email), TTY: 1-877-515-5559 (TTY number). Visit the Social Media Hub for more information. Winter 2024 program delivery details can be found on the website. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
